fluence.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 0aChurch historyyMiddle Ages, 600-1500. 0aChurch historyyPrimitive and early church, ca. 30-600. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300158878423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300158878/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles